snippet: A map on Friday with an article about research on the chances of an earthquake at the Hayward Fault in Northern California misspelled the name of a city along the fault. It is Fremont, not Freemont....
lead_paragraph: A map on Friday with an article about research on the chances of an earthquake at the Hayward Fault in Northern California misspelled the name of a city along the fault. It is Fremont, not Freemont.
abstract: Correction of map accompanying August 18 article about research on chances of an earthquake at Hayward Fault in Northern California
